snippet.title: Transistor - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Discover the world of Transistor, a sci-fi-themed action RPG from the creators of Bastion. 
More at: http://www.supergiantgames.com   |  @SupergiantGames

Song: "We All Become", from the Transistor Original Soundtrack.
Written by Darren Korb, vocals by Ashley Barrett
